The main change is to load 'custom-elements-es5-adapter.js' conditionally, so that it doesn't need to be included in the test suite.
This can be done by adding a { included: false } option to the file being loaded and then loading the file only when needed using the following code:
```javascript
if (window.customElements) {
  importScripts('../node_modules/@webcomponents/webcomponentsjs/custom-elements-es5-adapter.js');
}
```
This will ensure that 'custom-elements-es5-adapter.js' is only loaded if needed, and not included in the test suite.
